<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要开始了呢，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="40" />
这场名为<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />
钓鱼大赛的战斗<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />战斗的对手？<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的敌人别无其他，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是你自己<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />最近，用虚假情报引起对方兴趣，<delay20 />
以对方的反应为乐一事，<delay20 />
也被叫做“钓鱼”呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="4" />！
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们要<delay8 />不受表面情报所惑，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来进行真正的钓鱼吧？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起钓鱼这件事啊，<delay20 />
就好像恋爱的拉锯战呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果鱼儿扯线了，<delay20 />
不要因为心急立刻拉杆，<delay20 />
要安静地等一等<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再过一会儿，<delay20 />
鱼就会热情起来，进入认真模式，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就在此时拉起钓竿哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没错，就好像恋爱<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当然有的时候也会不顺利啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />钓鱼大赛只要在规定时间内<delay20 />
钓起尽可能多的鱼就行啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是说，<delay8 />
就算带着很多事先钓到的鱼，<delay20 />
也是毫无意义的哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想参加钓鱼大赛，<delay20 />
